<h2>How Share of Model Visibility Works</h2>
<h3>The Formula</h3>
<p>The calculation is straightforward:</p>
<p><strong>Share of Model = (Your brand mentions / Total brand mentions in category) × 100</strong></p>
<p>For example, if you ask 100 category-relevant questions to ChatGPT and your brand appears in 15 responses while all competitors combined appear in 100 total mentions, your share of model is 15%.</p>
<h3>What Gets Measured</h3>
<p>Share of model tracks 4 components across AI platforms:</p>
